[[File:Teatro María Guerrero (Madrid) 01.jpg|thumb|[[Teatro María Guerrero]]]]
The '''Centro Dramático Nacional''' ("National Drama Centre" or CDN) is a [[Madrid]]-based theatre company, operating under the [[Instituto de las Artes Escénicas y de la Música]] (Institute for Performing Arts and Music), an autonomous body of the [[Ministry of Culture (Spain)|Spanish Ministry of Culture]]. It is headquartered in two theatres: the [[Teatro María Guerrero]] and the [[Teatro Valle-Inclán]].

